metadata.name: Saturn Series #1
metadata.description:
'Saturn' is a utopian future where AI has solved human division for good, going against the dystopian narrative that has prevailed on media over the last couple of decades. The project tells a story of unlimited energy, interstellar travel, and time manipulation within the real bounds of our universe.
 The NFTs are curated result of experiments with prompt engineering for designing characters and environments. Inspired from a variety of sources as well as new imaginations. All images have been generated with artificial intelligence and curated by 0xCassini.eth
